Center for English Proficiency . The campus is located in Dubai City nearby Dubai Media City and Dubai Internet City . This article does not cite any references or sources . Please help ] improve this article ] by adding citations to reliable sources . Unverifiable material may be challenged and removed . American InterContinental University is accredited by the Commission on Colleges of the Southern Association of Colleges and Schools to award Associate , Bachelor’s , and Master’s degrees . This umbrella accreditation includes all approved branch campuses of the University , including AUD operating in Dubai . However the Southern Association of Colleges and Schools has changed the acrreditation status of American InterContinental University and all its branches to " probation " for noncompliance with accreditation standards . Furthermore , the University 's concentrations in Marketing Communications and Advertising ( Creative ) have been accredited by the International Advertising Association ( IAA ) in New York . The university enrolls both international and domestic students . In 2006 , Cherie Blair was the keynote speaker for the graduation cermeony of the Class of 2006 . 